(255, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/05/wordpress-4-2-2/''>WordPress 4.2.2 Security and Maintenance Release</a> <span class="rss-date">7 mayo, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.2.2 is now available. This is a critical security release for all previous versions and we strongly encourage you to update your sites immediately. Version 4.2.2 addresses two security issues: The Genericons icon font package, which is used in a number of popular themes and plugins, contained an HTML file vulnerable to a cross-site [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/learn-how-to-utilize-the-wp-rest-api-with-rachel-baker''>WPTavern: Learn How to Utilize the WP REST API with Rachel Baker</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wordpress-trainer-morten-rand-hendriksen-on-common-pain-points-roadblocks-and-advice-for-new-users''>WPTavern: WordPress Trainer Morten Rand-Hendriksen on Common Pain Points, Roadblocks, and Advice for New Users</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wordpress-org-is-testing-international-theme-and-plugin-directories''>WPTavern: WordPress.org is Testing International Theme and Plugin Directories</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Plugin popular:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-wp/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>MailChimp for WordPress</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=mailchimp-for-wp&amp;_wpnonce=3e8bf0db4a&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''MailChimp for WordPress''>Instalar</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
